      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Better Enrollment Options Protect Employee Needs Act or the Be Open Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Labor Standards Act of 1938 to repeal the requirement that employers with more than 200 full-time employees that offer enrollment in one or more health benefits plans automatically enroll all new full-time employees in one of those plans.</p>]]></text>
